t of the English copula be and the Indonesian copulas ada and adalah. The lingusitic description is done in a generative DM-based approach. Thus, this volume does not only provide new insights in the field language acquisiton, but also in the generative description of Indonesian in general and non-verbal predicates in particular.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Feb 2023) 4aEnglisch. 4aIndonesisch. 4aKopula. 4aNichtverbale Prädikate. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / General.2bisacsh  aCopula.  aGrammar Competition.  aIndonesian.  aNon-Verbal Predicates.  aSecond Language Acquisition.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2023 Part 1z978311117578208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDe Gruyter Mouton eBook Package 2023z978311120579308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishz978311099389908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022z9783110994810oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Linguistics 2022 Englishz978311099370708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Linguistics 2022z9783110993684oZDB-23-DSP08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertMouton eBook Package 2022z97831107912970 cEPUBz97831107663700 cprintz978311076625740uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311076633240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110766332423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110766332/original  a978-3-11-079129-7  Mouton eBook Package 2022b2022  a978-3-11-099370-7  EBOOK PACKAGE Linguistics 2022 Englishb2022  a978-3-11-099389-9  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishb2022  a978-3-11-117578-2  DG Plus DeG Package 2023 Part 1b2023  a978-3-11-120579-3  De Gruyter Mouton eBoo